{"text_id":255744,"tokens":["In"," this"," study",","," we"," present"," a"," novel"," approach"," for"," measuring"," electric"," fields"," generated"," by"," surface"," contaminants"," using"," neutral"," atoms","."," The"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," stems"," from"," the"," need"," to"," accurately"," quantify"," electric"," fields"," at"," the"," nanos","cale",","," which"," is"," crucial"," for"," understanding"," various"," physical",","," chemical",","," and"," biological"," processes","."," Our"," methodology"," utilizes"," a"," beam"," of"," neutral"," atoms",","," which"," are"," sensitive"," to"," electric"," fields",","," to"," probe"," the"," surface"," of"," interest","."," By"," measuring"," the"," deflection"," of"," the"," atom"," beam",","," we"," can"," determine"," the"," electric"," field"," strength"," and"," its"," spatial"," distribution",".","\n\n","The"," key"," idea"," behind"," our"," approach"," is"," that"," surface"," contaminants",","," such"," as"," charged"," molecules"," or"," atoms",","," can"," create"," measurable"," electric"," fields","."," These"," fields",","," in"," turn",","," affect"," the"," trajectory"," of"," neutral"," atoms"," passing"," nearby","."," By"," carefully"," controlling"," the"," atom"," beam"," and"," surface"," conditions",","," we"," can"," discern"," the"," electric"," fields"," generated"," by"," even"," minute"," quantities"," of"," surface"," contaminants",".","\n\n","Our"," results"," demonstrate"," the"," feasibility"," and"," sensitivity"," of"," this"," method","."," We"," have"," shown"," that"," it"," is"," capable"," of"," detecting"," electric"," fields"," generated"," by"," a"," single"," charged"," molecule",","," highlighting"," its"," potential"," for"," high","-","resolution"," electric"," field"," mapping","."," Furthermore",","," we"," have"," applied"," this"," technique"," to"," characterize"," electric"," fields"," on"," silicon"," surfaces"," with"," varying"," levels"," of"," contamination",","," revealing"," a"," direct"," correlation"," between"," surface"," cleanliness"," and"," the"," strength"," of"," the"," measured"," electric"," fields","."," Overall",","," our"," work"," introduces"," a"," powerful"," tool"," for"," characterizing"," electric"," fields"," at"," the"," nanos","cale"," and"," provides"," insights"," into"," the"," impact"," of"," surface"," contaminants"," on"," these"," fields","."," This"," advancement"," has"," implications"," for"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," disciplines",","," from"," surface"," science"," and"," nano","electronics"," to"," plas","mon","ics"," and"," electro","chemistry","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}